# 懵然不知

(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue: 唔知咗咗，唔知咗咗。 (lau4 bing1 coeng4 jau5 hou2 do1 sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng:confused (no knowledge)

<eg>
yue: 我係個學生，但係我唔知咗咗，唔知咗咗。 (lau4 bing1 coeng4 jau5 hou2 do1 sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng: I am a student, but I am not knowing anything.

<explanation>
yue: 我係個學生，但係我唔知咗咗，唔知咗咗。 (lau4 bing1 coeng4 jau5 hou2 do1 sai3 man1 zai2.)
eng: I am a student, but I am not knowing anything. [end of text]


